Joel Chukwuma Obi known as Joel Obi, who plays as a midfielder for Chievo Verona, has taken to his Instagram account @joelobi22 to announce the birth of his daughter. This is the third child he is having a child. It seems he intends to make it the last because he describes her arrival as the “perfect finishing to a beautiful family”. His post reads: “Welcome to the world little princess. You are the perfect finishing touch to our beautiful family”